{"tid":2388258,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"53歲台積電女組長偷吃2同事 綠帽夫蒐證怒索200萬賠償","createTime":"2021-01-31T03:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T04:20:27.000Z","uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"287e2731436005dcc3a30350a5ff7d8ae7a63856","tid":2388258,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210131/DKO36NQBCNHJ5L3K5P76XESYSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210131%2FDKO36NQBCNHJ5L3K5P76XESYSE%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWshAN7np5IU55thb9t6%2Bojg%3D&h=140502a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210131%2FDKO36NQBCNHJ5L3K5P76XESYSE%2F&h=4256555a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210131/DKO36NQBCNHJ5L3K5P76XESYSE/</a><br />\n<br />\n誰受得了老婆一次讓老公戴兩頂綠帽！台積電1名女組長去年同時出軌2同事，人夫去年3月先發現妻子與黃男疑似車震，赫見妻與小王在車上衣衫不整關係曖昧；接著妻連5日到鄭姓小王租屋處，頻繁進出鄭租屋處，人夫主張2男已侵害他配偶權，怒向法官提損害賠償，各索賠200萬元。<br />\n<br />\n雖2男均否認與台積電女組長有不倫關係，但法官調查後認為，鄭男雖主張在租屋處談台積電的專案秘密，但鄭卻不知避嫌，讓女組長到其租屋處，且長達10小時以上，認定已超越男女洽公關係，侵害到人夫的配偶權，因此判鄭男需賠償15萬元；而疑似與女組長車震的黃男，因事證不足被判免賠。"},{"pid":"4d2c43fbf9aa18de823194e32d609ad074979591","tid":2388258,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"52歲魏姓人夫表示，他與台積電的黃姓女組長（53歲）結婚29年，<span class=\"green\">沒想到妻子竟是花蝴蝶，去年3月間跟蹤妻子，發現她車子停在黃姓男同事的車旁，還走進到對方車內，坐在後座。他氣得上前拍打車窗，黃男驚嚇開窗，發現妻子坐在車內，2人倉惶整理衣褲，黃女在車內大叫「我要跟你離婚」，讓他傷心離開。</span><br />\n後來魏姓人夫發現，妻子有金山東街停車繳費單，加上妻子深夜未歸，去年4月1日愚人節前往金山東街埋伏，發現妻子停在該處過夜。而她也出沒在附近的公寓，並長時間逗留，<span class=\"red\">公寓住戶發現他抓姦，熱心提供監視錄影，他才發現妻子竟與鄭男同居一室。魏姓人夫事後查看行車紀錄器，發現妻子竟同時出軌黃、鄭2男，讓他精神崩潰，要求黃、鄭2男各賠200萬元。</span>"},{"pid":"9960996e11ed8f0c15ba5ccb170775ea92bba55e","tid":2388258,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:51:31.000Z","msg":"唔怪得TSM世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f6de0bd8a98df71d87feabc8adcd01d48f36ea","tid":2388258,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"淫殘不能移"},{"pid":"6722054104595cd7e9d8e5d0494fdbc033cf40db","tid":2388258,"uid":74361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"all in tsm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b9493349363732a36ca8c354e768d807ef30ac","tid":2388258,"uid":45007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"In tsm we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4d3b61b47807068f91c621a4bf9a6e42e22eee","tid":2388258,"uid":76804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEGW1WD.jpg&amp;h=2c0ba3e4&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"4bc93b9100cdee9aecc29f11e0058e87ca3afc86","tid":2388258,"uid":22893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:00:15.000Z","msg":"阿姨.jpg"},{"pid":"c291ed2a1f2c127dfe5bdb657b1ed8b26669735d","tid":2388258,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"何處無風化"}]}